    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Justus Wanzala</title>
    <description>Justus Wanzala is a Kenyan freelance journalist and development issues who writes about sustainable development, climate change, science policy, human rights  as well urban and rural development. He contributes articles to a number of publications with a global readership and also works as a development consultant. He has won several media fellowships and travelled widely. He is fluent in English and Swahili.
</description>
